ther imposing some restrictions on the values of the model parameters, or\nstudying limiting cases, in which the self-consistent equation is solved.\nImplications for the equivalence of ensembles have been discussed as well.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 19 Sep 2020 18:40:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-28"}
