d methods can surprisingly converge within a few iterations and\noutperform all competing methods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 20 Sep 2020 10:35:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 9 Oct 2020 16:21:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-12"}
